                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Hi Alex,",
                  "lineHeight": 1.6,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "UQzwf",
                  "name": "edP2",
                  "fill": "$wm-text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Thanks for sharing the roadmap. The priorities look solid. A few thoughts:\n\n- API v1: Can we include webhook support in the initial launch? It's been a top request from developers.\n- Dashboard: Agreed on real-time tracking. Let's also add export to CSV.\n- Mobile: Should we consider React Native for faster cross-platform dev?\n\nHappy to discuss on our Thursday sync.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "fontFamily": "Inter",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
