              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Hi Alex,\n\nGreat points on the roadmap. I agree that webhook support should be in the API v2 launch — it's been a top request from our enterprise clients.\n\nFor the mobile MVP, I suggest we focus on:\n• Email reading + compose\n• Push notifications\n• Basic search\n\nWe can add folders and filters in the follow-up release. Let's align on this during Thursday's sync.",
